General: This
executive order, just as the
first executive

00:12.913 --> 00:17.184 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
order, is a lawful and proper
exercise of
presidential authority.

00:17.217 --> 00:22.522 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JOHN YANG: The Trump
administration unveils
a revised travel ban after the
first was blocked

00:22.556 --> 00:23.790 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
