House's agenda
for the week.

28:31.376 --> 28:36.315 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's time for Politics Monday
with Amy Walter
of The Cook Political Report and
Tamara Keith

28:36.348 --> 28:37.449 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
of NPR.

28:37.482 --> 28:40.786 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Tam, you were one of the radio
poolers this
weekend.

28:40.819 --> 28:44.389 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You went with Trump down to
Mar-a-Lago in
Florida.

28:44.423 --> 28:45.691 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
