28:45.724 --> 28:47.459 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

28:47.492 --> 28:48.961 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH, National Public
Radio: Yes,
I think we were expecting it to
be a quiet

28:48.994 --> 28:50.429 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
weekend.

28:50.462 --> 28:53.098 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There weren't a lot of aides
that came down
with him on Air Force One.

28:53.131 --> 28:57.869 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But by the end of the weekend,
there were
a lot of people at Mar-a-Lago
meeting with

28:57.903 --> 29:01.740 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
President Trump all of a sudden.

29:01.773 --> 29:07.746 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Those tweets came out of the
darkness of morning
and changed the weekend for
sure.

29:07.779 --> 29:09.247 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOHN YANG: What do you make of
it?

29:09.281 --> 29:11.683 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Where did it come from, do you
think?

29:11.717 --> 29:14.486 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH: Well, it is
unclear.

29:14.519 --> 29:17.856 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If you ask the White House, they
won't say
where it came from.

29:17.889 --> 29:23.562 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If you put some dots together,
it looks like
it came from a Breitbart story
that rounded

29:23.595 --> 29:28.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
up that Mark Levin talk show and
various other
news reports that are out there.

29:28.066 --> 29:30.602 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And the White House keeps
pointing to reports.

29:30.636 --> 29:33.005 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I started asking at 7:00 a.m.

29:33.038 --> 29:34.706 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Saturday.

29:34.740 --> 29:37.409 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the questions continue,
where exactly
is the president getting this
from?

29:37.442 --> 29:38.744 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He's the president of the United
States.

29:38.777 --> 29:42.547 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It's possible he could be
getting intelligence
